                     <handNote scope="major" script="nasta_liq" medium="ink">A majority of folios in
                        the written in clear <material>black</material> nasta‘līq with occasional
                        red markings in the appendices. </handNote>
                     <handNote scope="minor" script="nasta_liq" medium="ink">Folios <locus
